Former SNB Head Roth Is ‘Pessimistic’ on Europe, L’Hebdo Reports

-- B y   T h o m a s   M u l i e r
-- 
2011-09-15T06:27:25Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/former-snb-head-roth-is-pessimistic-on-europe-l-hebdo-reports.html
Jean-Pierre Roth, the former
president of the  Swiss National Bank , said he’s “very
pessimistic” about  Europe ’s economy as governments struggle to
contain the region’s debt crisis,  L’Hebdo  reported.  Historians will judge this period as a “total failure” of
European leadership, Roth told the magazine in the interview
published today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Thomas Mulier in Geneva at 
